    file: 'services/market-data/src/services/paper_trading_engine.py · services/decision-engine/src/api/routes.py · services/signal-engine/src/api/routes.py',
    effort: '1.5h',
    impact: 'High — three bugs were causing real trading damage: (1) paper trading re-entered stocks immediately after a stop loss, compounding losses on the same declining stock (2382.HK lost 3 trades in sequence within 1 hour, all stops). (2) Decision engine was broken for all HK trades due to a timezone mismatch, forcing every HK entry through the weaker _should_enter() fallback instead of the full DE scoring. (3) Manual Refresh on the stock detail page was overwriting catalyst-adjusted bullish_probability with the raw unadjusted value (bug #2 from T176 audit).',
